      "entryThesis": "This trade sold exposure to the specific 95-96\u00b0 temperature range because the model's edge indicated the market was overpricing that outcome, expecting probabilities to be lower than the 58% implied by the entry price. The strategy claimed a negative model edge (-0.3564), suggesting the contract's fair value was below the entry price, making it a candidate to sell. However, the position hit a stop-loss in under an hour, indicating the market moved sharply against this thesis, likely as real-time weather data or forecasts shifted.",
